V!Register your participation\u000a!!!!You have completed the training!\u000aCongratulations! Much of the information you've read through will continue to be useful while you're abroad and once you return home. After you register your participation, click through to the end and ''bookmark the Index page''--you'll be able to easily go back and read any information in this presentation! Also, don't forget to download GEO's [[Traveler Checklist|https://geo.vanderbilt.edu/_customtags/ct_FileRetrieve.cfm?File_ID=14068]] to help you keep track of many of the things you need to do next.\u000a\u000aIf you are a student, please ''register your participation'' in this training by clicking on the button below! Fill in your name and email address, then submit the form. Note that it may take a few days before your registration is reflected on your GEO account.\u000a\u000a<div id="registration"><a target="_blank" href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSctpIhHe4POdUH68s19ccalPUlq5UjZ1nEoo7gbXeu3ojQyZg/viewform?usp=sf_link"><<button "Register your participation">><</button>></a></div>\u000a/% <<if storage.getItem("registration") neq true>><div id="registration"><<button "Register your participation">><<if $UAinfo.os.name eq "Android" or $UAinfo.os.name eq "iOS" or $UAinfo.os.name eq "IE" or config.historyMode eq HistoryMode.Hash or $browserSupport eq "no" or isHandheld() eq true>><<run window.open('https://form.jotformpro.com/form/41326113066949','blank','scrollbars=yes,toolbar=no,width=700,height=500');>>ePDO Registration</a><<else>><<run showRegistration(); registrationUpdate();>><</if>><</button>></div>\u000a<iframe id="JotFormIFrame" onload="registrationInit();" allowtransparency="true" src="Register/registration.html" frameborder="0" scrolling="no"></iframe>\u005c\u000a<<script>>\u000a//Code from JotForm\u000awindow.handleIFrameMessage=function(e){var t=e.data.split(":");console.log(t[0] + t[1]);var n=document.getElementById("JotFormIFrame");if(!n)return;switch(t[0]){case"scrollIntoView":n.scrollIntoView();break;case"setHeight":n.style.height=t[1]+"px";break}};if(window.addEventListener){window.addEventListener("message",handleIFrameMessage,false)}else if(window.attachEvent){window.attachEvent("onmessage",handleIFrameMessage)}\u000a<</script>>\u005c\u000a<<else>>\u005c\u000a<div class="message-box success"><div class="message-box-symbol"></div><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;You have successfully registered your participation!</span></div>\u000a<</if>> %/ \u005c\u000aIf you have trouble submitting the registration form, please go [[here|https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSctpIhHe4POdUH68s19ccalPUlq5UjZ1nEoo7gbXeu3ojQyZg/viewform?usp=sf_link]].\u000a\u000aOnce you've registered, you may want to check out the next couple of pages, which include ''credits'' for the student photographs and other pieces that went into making this training document, as well as the bookmarkable ''index'' that  will allow you to come back and navigate to any page in the presentation.\u000a\u000aRemember, if you have questions about your next steps or any other aspect of your study abroad experience, GEO staff are standing by! [[Contact us|https://vanderbilt.edu/geo/advising/]].\u000a\u000a<<segue "Credits">>\u005c
